---
title: Pork Schnitzel & Katsu Sauce Burger with Potato Wedges & Creamy Slaw
description: The golden crunch of a crumbed pork schnitzel between buttery soft buns can never be beaten. Dazzle at the dinner table with
two superb sauces, a dark katsu sauce for the pork and a creamy mayo to elevate the slaw to new heights.
